td.p:
The Zakon za danak varhu dobavenata stoynost (Law on Value Added Tax, DV No 63, of 4 August 2006; ‘the ZDDS’) entered into force on 1 January 2007, the date on which the Treaty between the Member States of the European Union and the Republic of Bulgaria and Romania, concerning the accession of the Republic of Bulgaria and Romania to the European Union (
OJ 2005 L 157, p. 11
) also entered into force.
